### ==========================================================
### Auction Platform - API Testing
### Bisa dijalankan langsung dari VS Code (extension "REST Client")
### atau JetBrains Rider (built-in HTTP Client)
### ==========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### AUTH
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register user baru (Bidder)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testbidder@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "fullName": "Test Bidder",
  "role": "Bidder"
}

### Register user baru (Seller)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testseller@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "fullName": "Test Seller",
  "role": "Seller"
}
### Register User Salah
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "emailtidakvalid@example.com",
  "password": "123",
  "fullName": "",
  "role": "Superadmin"
}

### Login BIDDER - JWT akan otomatis tersimpan di HttpOnly Cookie
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testbidder@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Login SELLER - JWT akan otomatis tersimpan di HttpOnly Cookie
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testseller@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Cek user yang sedang login (butuh cookie dari login di atas)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout


### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### AUCTIONS
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List semua lelang (default: Active + Scheduled)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auctions

### List lelang dengan filter status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auctions?status=Inactive

### List lelang dengan search judul
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auctions/my-selling

### List lelang dengan pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auctions?page=1&pageSize=5

### Detail lelang (ganti id dengan hasil dari GET /api/auctions)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auctions/cf2c217e-c6b3-4595-9e6b-d984d80b6c39

### Cancel auction (login sebagai seller)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/auctions/{auctionId}

### Buat lelang baru (butuh login sebagai Seller dan punya itemId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auctions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": "b6136eb5-0c16-4bf9-b121-93cd65b8213",
  "startingPrice": 5000000,
  "reservePrice": null,
  "bidIncrement": 50000,
  "buyNowPrice": null,
  "startTime": "2026-07-06T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-07-10T10:00:00Z"
}

### Place bid (butuh login sebagai Bidder, ganti auctionId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auctions/ddb0522b-a708-4574-af3f-5bb439beacfa/bids
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 4500000
}

### Cek saldo wallet (butuh login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet

### Top up saldo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/topup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000000
}

### List kategori (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories

### Buat item baru (login sebagai seller dulu)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": "91e19ffe-4350-4741-a2a7-be5d918ffa47",
  "title": "Parfum",
  "description": "Parfum",
  "condition": "Used",
  "imageUrls": ["https://picsum.photos/seed/parfum1/400/300"]
}

### List item saya (login sebagai seller)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/mine